            <title>[HIVE-16336] Rename hive.spark.use.file.size.for.mapjoin to hive.spark.use.ts.stats.for.mapjoin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-16336</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The name &lt;tt&gt;hive.spark.use.file.size.for.mapjoin&lt;/tt&gt; is confusing. It indicates that HoS uses file size for mapjoin but in fact it still uses (in-memory) data size. We should change it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
